Invocation Name: magic sounds vacuum
des:
Use vacuum sound from Sound Sleeper app to get to sleep easily and to sleep soundly through the night. Help your baby get to sleep quickly without fuss, and get your own zzz's too. 
 
This high-quality natural sound will gently lull you to sleep, and is also effective at blocking outside noise so nothing disturbs you.
 
If you have any questions or comments, please drop us a line at soundsleeperapp@gmail.com, or give us a call at 1-857-239-0882. 
We’ll be very glad to hear from you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
